snippet.title: Amber Heard at The Worth It Show by L'Oréal Paris in TIFF
snippet.description:
All the credits of the video goes to L'Oréal Paris. We don't own this material and we promote this only for entertainment.
We do not aim at profit.

L'Oréal Paris brand ambassadors Andie MacDowell and Amber Heard, along with Shohreh Agdashloo, ambassador for Share Her Journey, TIFF's movement promoting women in film, shared a thoughtful conversation about the importance of women in the cinamatografic industry.
